Uzalo and Skeem Saam crossover brought mixed emotions to the world of Twitter. SABC 1 had been showing an ad about the crossover for a couple of weeks now and it has finally happened. The two soapies which, are some of the most loved stories in Mzansi merged on Tuesday with Mxolisi, played by Nay Maps making an appearance on Skeem Saam. In the story, Mxolisi leaves Uzalo to escape the prison and flees to Mozambique. Some tweeps were excited while some just did not want him to be there.        